sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant HttpServer
    participant App
    participant Routes
    participant HealthHandler
    participant PlaceholderHandler

    Note over Client,PlaceholderHandler: Health Check Request Flow
    Client->>HttpServer: GET /api/health
    HttpServer->>App: Route request
    App->>Routes: configure_routes
    Routes->>HealthHandler: health_check()
    HealthHandler-->>Routes: {"status": "ok"}
    Routes-->>App: HttpResponse 200
    App-->>HttpServer: Response
    HttpServer-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Client,PlaceholderHandler: Placeholder Route Flow
    Client->>HttpServer: GET /api/users
    HttpServer->>App: Route request
    App->>Routes: configure_routes
    Routes->>PlaceholderHandler: user_routes
    PlaceholderHandler-->>Routes: HttpResponse 501
    Routes-->>App: Not Implemented
    App-->>HttpServer: Response
    HttpServer-->>Client: 501 Not Implemented

